      <h1>Best Life Insurance Companies (2026) &mdash; Coverage &amp; Rates Compared</h1>
      <p class="article-intro">Choosing a life insurance company is a decision that could affect your family for decades. Unlike switching car insurers or bank accounts, a life insurance policy is a long-term contract, and you need the company behind it to be financially rock-solid 30 or 40 years from now when a claim is actually filed. This guide compares ten of the strongest life insurance companies in the United States across financial strength ratings, policy offerings, pricing, and best-fit scenarios so you can narrow your search with confidence.</p>
